      • gameOver

        public void gameOver(java.awt.Graphics g)
        Game ending method

        After the game is over, clean up the interface elements and prompt "Game Over!"

      • draw

        public void draw(java.awt.Graphics g)
        Painter method

        Judging the survival status of the home and whether it is red

        • • If the home is alive and red, draw a red square picture and set the blood lineHome.DrawBloodbBar.draw(Graphics)
        • If the home is alive and blue, draw a blue crystal picture and set the blood lineHome.DrawBloodbBar.draw(Graphics)
        • If the home is not alive and is red, draw the "Victory" font and call the gameOver(Graphics) function.
        • If the home is not alive and is blue, draw the "Defeat" font and call the gameOver(Graphics) function.
        参数:
        g - Brush tool
